### User Endpoints (existing)

# Get all users
GET http://localhost:3000/users

###

# Get user by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/users/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011

###

# Create new user
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "password": "securepass123",
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "age": 28,
  "role": "user"
}

###

# Update user
PATCH http://localhost:3000/users/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Jane Updated",
  "age": 29
}

###

# Delete user
DELETE http://localhost:3000/users/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011

